      <a class="profession-card" href="https://stairwaymortgage.com/sales-professionals/financial-advisor-sales/">
        <div class="profession-num">06</div>
        <h3 class="profession-title">Financial Advisors (Sales)</h3>
        <p class="profession-tag">"I&rsquo;m at a wirehouse. My production grid pays oddly. The lender is confused."</p>
        <ul class="profession-points">
          <li>Wirehouse W-2 with production-grid commission structure</li>
          <li>Broker-dealer 1099 with grid payout history</li>
          <li>Recurring fee income (managed accounts) treated as continuous</li>
