      </a>

      <a class="profession-card" href="https://stairwaymortgage.com/sales-professionals/yacht-broker/">
        <div class="profession-num">07</div>
        <h3 class="profession-title">Yacht Brokers</h3>
        <p class="profession-tag">"One sale every two months. Each one moves the needle. The lender averages it wrong."</p>
        <ul class="profession-points">
          <li>1099 commission with co-brokerage split history</li>
          <li>Central-listing override and charter commission mix</li>
          <li>Bank-statement program when sales cycle is long</li>
          <li>South Florida yacht-market specialization (cross-link from <a href="https://stairwaymortgage.com/yacht-professionals/" style="color: var(--ink);">Yacht Professionals hub</a>)</li>
        </ul>
        <span class="profession-link">Read the yacht broker mortgage guide</span>
      </a>
      </div>
    </div>
