          <li>&rarr; <a href="https://stairwaymortgage.com/sales-professionals/financial-advisor-sales/">Financial advisor mortgage guide</a> &mdash; transition deals, forgivable notes, deferred bonus</li>
          <li>&rarr; <a href="https://stairwaymortgage.com/corporate-executives/">Corporate Executives hub</a> &mdash; for senior leadership tracks beyond pure sales</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
