        <p>Specialty pharmaceutical sales rep, promoted to senior territory in March with OTE jumping from $175K to $290K. Two big-bank lenders averaged her last two years of W-2s and qualified her at the old number. We pulled the new comp plan, requested an employer attestation letter confirming the territory upgrade was permanent, and routed the file to a lender that accepts trailing-12 plus current-run-rate income on documented promotions. Approved at the right number. Closed on a Boca Raton 4-bed in 28 days. No surprises at the table.</p>
      </div>
